The '''Fractal Heresy''' was an event that took place sometime around the formation of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. It proved many of the [[Givin/Legends|Givin]] beliefs false, and thus, many Givin priests left their religious orders, including [[Chrag'mak'al]], who became a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]].

